دة</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">التحضير للزيارة وإكمال النماذج</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">عملية تسجيل الوصول مع التحديثات والتأكيدات</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">المتابعة بعد الزيارة وجمع الملاحظات</span></li></ul></div><div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4">الفوترة والمدفوعات</h3><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">حساب تلقائي للرسوم بناءً على الخدمات</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">معالجة مطالبات التأمين والتسوية</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">فوترة المرضى مع بيانات مفصلة</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">معالجة الدفع عبر الإنترنت مع خيارات متعددة</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">تأكيد